TI  - Unsupervised machine learning for flaw detection in automated ultrasonic testing of carbon fibre reinforced plastic composites
T2  - ULTRASONICS
LA  - English
KW  - Automated defect detection
KW  - Machine learning
KW  - Deep learning in ultrasonic testing
KW  - Non-destructive evaluation
KW  - Carbon fibre reinforced polymers
