TI  - Investigation of calendaring parameters on the microstructure of graphite anodes within lithium-ion batteries: Insights from ultrasonic testing
T2  - JOURNAL OF POWER SOURCES
LA  - English
KW  - Lithium-ion batteries
KW  - Cell instrumentation
KW  - Ultrasonic/acoustic sensing
KW  - Battery manufacturing
KW  - Digitalisation in battery manufacturing
KW  - CHARGE
