TI  - Multi-feature recognition of weld defects with an ultrasonic signal-image-joint machine learning fusion model☆
T2  - ENGINEERING APPLICATIONS OF ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE
LA  - English
KW  - Ultrasonic testing
KW  - Weld defects
KW  - Multi-feature recognition
