TI  - Delamination Defects Localization Using a New Time Frequency Algorithm Based on S-Transform for Ultrasonic Testing of Wind Turbine Blades Composite Materials
T2  - RUSSIAN JOURNAL OF NONDESTRUCTIVE TESTING
LA  - English
KW  - composite materials
KW  - wind turbine blades
KW  - ultrasonic signal
KW  - modified Stockwell transform
