TI  - Three-Dimensional Ultrasonic Reverse-Time Migration Imaging of Submarine Pipeline Nondestructive Testing in Cylindrical Coordinates
T2  - JOURNAL OF MARINE SCIENCE AND ENGINEERING
LA  - English
KW  - submarine pipelines
