TI  - Measurement of Defect Sizes and Physical Limitations of Digital Data Processing in Ultrasonic Flaw Detection by Echo and Diffraction Methods
T2  - RUSSIAN JOURNAL OF NONDESTRUCTIVE TESTING
LA  - English
KW  - ultrasonic testing
KW  - defects in materials and welds
KW  - defect size
