TI  - Structural health monitoring of fastener hole using ring-design direct-write piezoelectric ultrasonic transducer
T2  - STRUCTURAL HEALTH MONITORING-AN INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL
LA  - English
KW  - direct-write
KW  - piezoelectric ultrasonic transducer
KW  - structural health monitoring
KW  - pulse-echo
