TI  - Controlling Wasserstein Distances by Kernel Norms with Application to Compressive Statistical Learning
T2  - JOURNAL OF MACHINE LEARNING RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - optimal transport
KW  - maximum mean discrepancy
KW  - statistical learning
KW  - compressive learning
