TI  - Localised ensemble learning (LEL) - a localised approach to class imbalance
T2  - PATTERN ANALYSIS AND APPLICATIONS
LA  - English
KW  - Class Imbalance
KW  - Classification
KW  - Random forest
KW  - Nearest neighbour
KW  - PERFORMANCE
KW  - ALGORITHMS
